cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and parsing. The use of convolutional neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The mention of graph linearization technique indicates that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of convolutional neural networks for image processing could suggest that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
